{"TopicId":184440,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Need a mod with fixed/static fairing sizes.","CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T17:10:45Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T17:10:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m trying to find a mod that has pre-set fairing sizes, like how it\u0027s done in real life.\u00A0 I want the size of the payloads to be restricted by the inner dimensions of the fairings, and to be forced to launch with a fairing that\u0027s hilariously too big for the payload (like Starman).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot having any luck searching.\u00A0 Googling for fixed fairing sizes just brings up threads of the hilarious broken fairing textures a few versions back.\u00A0 Static fairing sizes somehow got me to KWRocketry, which act the same as stock fairings,\u00A0 Procedural Fairings, which is the exact opposite of what I want, and Zero Point Fairings, which despite the Spacedock page listing it as updated for 1.6.1, the parts aren\u0027t loading for me in 1.7.0, and it\u0027s expressly stated that they don\u0027t protect from drag anyway in stock.\u00A0 (Needs \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)\u0022\u003EFAR\u003C/abbr\u003E or NEAR).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo does anyone know of any mod that provides pre-set fairing parts that occlude their payload correctly in stock?\u00A0 The fairing being actual parts that I can attach stuff too would be fantastic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis thing from BDB is pretty close, but I\u0027d like it more like a fairing, not a nose cone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022363screenshot223.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022609\u0022 src=\u0022http://u.cubeupload.com/Geonovast/363screenshot223.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T17:43:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know before fairings were stock, old, and I mean OLD versions of KW had fixed clamshell fairings.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 It may or may not till work as it was just a parts pack.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T17:51:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597885\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184440\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557683018\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know before fairings were stock, old, and I mean OLD versions of KW had fixed clamshell fairings.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 It may or may not till work as it was just a parts pack.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen did fairings become stock?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Barzon","CreatedById":185383,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T18:07:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8070377739\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/119171-140-old-school-fairings/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:225px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0I think this might be what you are looking for \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough it says 1.4, i am pretty sure it still works.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T18:08:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022179753\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Geonovast\u003C/a\u003E how about \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/159101-151-simple-adjustable-fairings-v110-bringing-back-the-kw-rocketry-fairings-with-enhancements/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003ESimple Adjustable Fairings?\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T18:41:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597891\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184440\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557683494\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n50 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen did fairings become stock?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nehhhhh..... .22ish?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T18:46:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/185383-barzon-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022185383\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/185383-barzon-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Barzon Kerman\u003C/a\u003E That looks ideal, since it\u0027s individual parts that I may be able to attach stuff like parachutes to, the parts are not loading for me in 1.7.0.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E That\u0027s nearly exactly what I wanted!\u00A0 Thank you!\u00A0 I was hoping to able to recover the fairings, but that wasn\u0027t huge.\u00A0 This should do nicely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597912\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184440\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557686517\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nehhhhh..... .22ish?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow.. that\u0027s quite a way back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLuckily SAF seems to hit the spot.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI couldn\u0027t even find a version of KW that was older than 1.1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T18:48:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597914\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184440\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557686785\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI couldn\u0027t even find a version of KW that was older than 1.1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, it was abandoned by the original creators a long time ago, that thread might be lost to the depths.....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T21:25:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597891\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184440\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557683494\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen did fairings become stock?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m pretty sure it was 1.0, when the atmosphere changed to make them useful.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m working on a mod idea (that will likely never see the light of day as I\u0027m both not playing a lot and am not a very good modder \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E )\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E where things start super expensive and get cheaper as you use them. It\u0027d be cool if the first use of a specific fairing (saved as a sub-assembly) was like 100 times the cost or more, then subsequent uses were normal cost.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen you could (and must) design your own fairings, but in most every single case it\u0027s better to use an already designed one over making a new one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the meantime, you could do the enforcing yourself. Make a few fairings per size, save them as sub-assemblies, and then use the janitor\u0027s closet to remove the fairings from the part list \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-12T21:29:42Z\u0022 title=\u002205/12/2019 09:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 12, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by 5thHorseman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketSquid","CreatedById":152665,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-16T21:36:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTundra industries has a fixed size fairing, based on the Falcon 9\u0027s fairing.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}